result.name: Yoshinoya

reviews.text: Opens 24 Hours which is convenient for late night meals. Quite a lot of customers which we need to wait for awhile before taking a seat. Standard Yoshinoya quality.
Reliable place for some Japanese style beef and chicken rice. Had hotpot here though, was satisfying as usual for a quick meal.
OK I am biased but I think it's simply happiness to have hot pot during overnight shift work! At least it's 24hr so you have other choices than Mcdonald or convenient store or cup noodles!
The food is great but the place is dirty. Especially the toilets. Very smelly and messy. No soap, no paper tissues.
Quality food & helpful staffs
